# Terraform
terraform/.terraform/          # downloaded provider binaries — do NOT commit
terraform/terraform.tfvars     # contains your GitHub token — do NOT commit
terraform/*.tfstate             # live state — do NOT commit (use remote state)
terraform/*.tfstate.backup
# Note: terraform/.terraform.lock.hcl SHOULD be committed (pins provider versions)
